en_428136_0	Hambantota-based 122 Brigade troops of the 12 Division of the Security Force Headquarters - Central with sponsorship provided by Udahamulla Sri Jinarathanarama temple, headed by Ven Kalavinne Dhammarakkitha Nayake Thero gave away packs of nutrients to 53 pregnant women and invoke blessings on them during a religious ceremony that got underway at Mattala Sri Wajirarama Maha Viharaya in Hambantota on Monday (30).
en_428136_1	This programme also provided a special lunch treat to all those pregnant women at the same location following arrangements that were made by 122 Brigade troops on the instructions of the 122 Brigade Commander.
